race.description: Follow Thedogssa On X (N/P) Tg 1-4W Series 3 F
race.comment: STORM SISTER (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at Gawler over 400m behind Cobalt Winter (24.24) in a TG1-4W. Scored at her previous run. Can bounce back. HAYRIDE RAMPS (8) missed the frame latest when fifth at this track (20.90) but was a winner three back in the second best time of the program. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Worth another chance. BILLY EXTRA (2) goes very well at the distance with two wins and a placing from five starts. Recorded a 0.8 lengths win (20.23) in a TG1-4W last time at this track. Among the main chances. DAME TRUCULENT (5) can run a bold race on best form.
